						<div class="postbody">I'm currently working on a sound engine, and I'm handling arpeggios and storing new values into $4002/$4003. However, this horrible bubbly sound comes from doing direct writes to $4002/$4003 every frame. How do most games avoid this? And what causes this?</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.freewebs.com/the_bott/" class="postlink">-Owner of Poultry Games</a></div>
