			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Write to $4003/7 only on new notes, but you can write to $4002 whenever you want to. If you do change the pitch and get beyond the 8-bit limits, then yes write to $4003/7, but you'll get a phase reset, which sounds bad on vibratoes (Mega Man 2 boss music). Blargg made a workarround for this using a lot of tricks with $4017 and $4001/5, but I don't know any emulator that supported it.
<br />On a side-hand, I've made a sound code which optionally enable wirting to $4003 every frame, to get a grumble effect on purpose.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
