					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">That's a lot like the idea I had for my (abandoned) music engine.  Except that every instrument was able to be multi-channel, it's not just for drums.  All the instruments would've had individual channel priorities.  Also there were some related effects such as single and multi-channel echo, with this priority system.  I had planned to also try out a volume-based priority system.
<br />
<br />These features are after spending years of tediously entering multichannel effects into NT2 and other trackers.  It would be a pain in the ass to do this stuff in straight MML also.</div>

